p.inserted: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

inserted.p: Providing for a joint session of Congress to receive a message from the President.

ul.p: Resolved by the House of Representatives (the Senate concurring), That the two Houses of Congress assemble in the Hall of the House of Representatives on Tuesday, February 12, 2013, at 9 p.m., for the purpose of receiving
such communication as the President of the United States shall be pleased to make to them.

body.p: Passed the House of Representatives February 4, 2013.

Clerk.
